---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - HoroTalk">

  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-primary-light to-white py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm text-text-light mb-2">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary">Home</a> &rsaquo; Privacy Policy
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-text-light text-sm">Last updated: April 14, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg max-w-none">

      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        HoroTalk ("we", "our", "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our WhatsApp-based astrology service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">When you use HoroTalk, we may collect the following information:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light text-sm mb-6">
        <li><strong>WhatsApp phone number</strong> — provided automatically when you message us</li>
        <li><strong>Birth details</strong> — date of birth, time of birth, and place of birth that you share for generating your Kundli</li>
        <li><strong>Chat messages</strong> — your questions and conversations with HoroTalk</li>
        <li><strong>Payment information</strong> — if you subscribe to a paid plan (processed through secure third-party payment providers)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">We use your information solely for the following purposes:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light text-sm mb-6">
        <li>Generating personalized astrology readings based on your birth chart</li>
        <li>Responding to your astrology questions and follow-ups</li>
        <li>Processing payments for premium subscriptions</li>
        <li>Improving our AI models and service quality</li>
        <li>Sending service-related notifications (e.g., subscription reminders)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">3. Data Storage & Security</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light text-sm mb-6">
        <li>Your birth details are stored securely on encrypted servers to provide ongoing personalized readings</li>
        <li>We do not store your WhatsApp messages beyond what is necessary to provide the service</li>
        <li>We use industry-standard encryption and security measures to protect your data</li>
        <li>Access to your data is restricted to authorized personnel only</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">4. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties, except:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light text-sm mb-6">
        <li>Payment processors — to handle subscription payments securely</li>
        <li>WhatsApp / Meta — as required by the WhatsApp Business Platform for message delivery</li>
        <li>Legal compliance — if required by Indian law or regulatory authorities</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">You have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light text-sm mb-6">
        <li><strong>Access</strong> your personal data stored with us</li>
        <li><strong>Delete</strong> your data — message us "Delete my data" on WhatsApp and we will erase all your stored information within 30 days</li>
        <li><strong>Opt out</strong> — stop using the service at any time by simply not messaging us</li>
        <li><strong>Correct</strong> your birth details by providing updated information</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">6. Cookies & Website Tracking</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        This website does not use cookies or third-party tracking scripts. We do not track your browsing activity.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        HoroTalk is not intended for use by individuals under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect information from children.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. Continued use of HoroTalk after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-2">
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or want to exercise your data rights:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light text-sm mb-6">
        <li><strong>WhatsApp</strong>: Message us directly</li>
        <li><strong>Email</strong>: hello@horotalk.in</li>
      </ul>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
